# Retention Technical Annexes

One file per application that processes data subject to retention rules
(LGPD, GDPR, contractual, regulatory).

## Naming
`<app-name>.md` — matches the app folder name in `applications/`.

## Per-app annex content

Each annex should specify:
- **Data categories** stored by the app
- **Retention period** per category
- **Deletion mechanism** (automatic job, manual, on-request)
- **Anonymization or hard-delete** policy
- **Legal basis** (links to LGPD matrix row)
- **Audit trail** (where deletions are logged)

See `_template.md` (when added) for the per-app template.
